title: Various Artists - Navigatorz Fresh!! Indie Playlist March 2014
description:
This is a fresh!! new!! Indie Playlist for March 2014.!! Many new songs, some of them great, waiting for you to give them a chance.If you like them please buy original CDs, digital song, Vinyl or stream and support the artists. 
Anyone who is interested in sending your own stuff (via links to downloads), we would gladly listen to your music and include it in our list or radio show if we find it good, so more people would hear it...This month as always, artwork is from our designer Luubenica. 

Best regards

Navigatorz team

NAVIGATOR, music team producing beats,grooves and much more...And an awesome DJ team and a soundsystem as well proudly presents:

NAVIGATORZ FRESH!! INDIE PLAYLIST MARCH 2014

NAVIGATORZ FRESH!! INDIE PLAYLIST contains the team's choice when it comes to independent music acts,ranging from guitar, electronic acts to so called "indietronica" Folk, Cover, Legends...and experimental sounds...

Enjoy!


P.S. You can WATCH our suggestion for best video on YOUTUBE.On the chanell of GLE Magazine our video playlist20 FRESH!!NEW!! VIDEOS!! SINGLES every month!!!

On our soundcloud profile you can find lot of our interesting remixes with download option. Visit our profiles and become our friend on: or
